    <title>Soul Time</title>
    <link>https://www.pbsfm.org.au/program/soul-time</link>
    <description>&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Soul Time has been on air since September 1984, and is the longest running soul show in the world. It is produced and hosted by Vince Peach.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Soul Time plays a mixture of Northern soul, Motown and related styles, from the sixties to the modern day.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Original R&amp;amp;B, southern grooves and funk are also featured on Soul Time as well as a weekly gig guide of whats on in Melbourne and the rest of Australia&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;vince.peach@yahoo.com&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

